&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;# Set SSH_AUTH_SOCK so that SSH will use gpg-agent instead of ssh-agent. Add this to tour bashprofile or zshrc&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
